Summary

Based in Sunnyvale, CA, eGain Communications is an eCRM vendor offering products designed to improve business with an enterprise's customers. The product line includes a Web-based architecture linking communication channels with critical business processes. The eGain Commerce suite manages customer interactions in live Web chat and collaboration, e-mail, and self-service channels. With the acquisition of Inference Corp., eGain picks up some key contact center and customer profiling tools to add to its own product line. The vendor boasts a base of more than 600 customers worldwide, including 3Com, CNN, MasterCard, Otis Elevator, and Verizon.




